{"tid":1984133,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MOMOLAND捐價值1億韓圜抗菌口罩套助抗疫","createTime":"2020-04-22T09:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T11:48:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e50b6714fbcfa84e0b474900fc0bc572a8c9630d","tid":1984133,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/04/200421001953100707-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F200421001953100707-600x400.jpg&h=ae8f2053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【大紀元2020年04月21日訊】（大紀元記者朝蓉編譯報導）今天（21日），韓國女團MOMOLAND透過國際救濟發展組織（NGO）「Korean Plan」捐出價值約1億韓圜（約265萬台幣／8.8萬美金）的抗菌口罩套給海內外的低收入戶，並於官方SNS表明她們希望能協助大家抵抗中共病毒（武漢肺炎）疫情的心情。<br />\n<br />\nMOMOLAND為了協助防疫，今天向NGO「Korean Plan」捐出約相當於1億韓圜的1萬個抗菌口罩套。對此她們表示：「想替因COVID-19（中共病毒）而感到辛苦的人們分擔痛苦，所以透過國際救濟發展組織『Korean Plan』捐贈了。」她們也表示，希望捐贈的這些抗菌口罩套，能讓人民面對病毒時都能保持安全。<br />\n<br />\n今天MOMOLAND也在官方SNS上傳6位成員分別與抗菌口罩套拍攝的合照，並寫下文字：「我們MOMOLAND也想在預防COVID-19（中共病毒）疫情上幫上一點忙，所以捐出了抗菌口罩套（WecanG）！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWGjbzIUYAI1K7F?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEWGjbzIUYAI1K7F%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=2981c9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她們也說：「應該知道口罩是必備品吧？我們Merry（官方粉絲名）也要注意健康！我們大家一起戰勝COVID-19吧！」並以Hashtag標註了全員「慧彬」、「JANE」、「娜允」、「珠伊」、「妸仁」、「Nancy」。<br />\n<br />\n自2016年起，MOMOLAND就作為NGO「Korean Plan」的宣傳大使，積極的開展協助全球兒童的贊助活動和宣傳活動等。這次面對全球性的中共病毒（武漢肺炎）疫情，MOMOLAND也透過「Korean Plan」捐出口罩套來協助海內外的低收入戶。<br />\n<br />\n另外， MOMOLAND所屬公司MLD娛樂也曾於12日在官方YouTube頻道公開去年底退出MOMOLAND的前團員妍雨（YEONWOO）唱跳的洗手歌《Rub and Wash Hands（쓱쓱싹싹）》。對此各國網友們也留言表示：「會聽妍雨的話」、「會好好洗手的」。"},{"pid":"5792eb97d8c1bf3a8755e37d34d9881f32918293","tid":1984133,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"&rarr;StressND: 不留一些錢嗎 感覺這團   <br />\n推 master32: 會捐這個額度的物資,表示有能力吧~  <br />\n推 pinklolipop: 她們竟然有辦法捐1億！？  <br />\n推 xiawu: 做好事推 <br />\n推 q251425: 團員不是還要還錢嗎 為什麼能捐  <br />\n推 rexlaser: 這團團員的負債感覺又增加了...  <br />\n推 manmani: 可能公司先代付再扣除收入吧  <br />\n推 wingfun: 她們負債還清了?    <br />\n推 iamseanx: 推難得一篇正面新聞！"},{"pid":"a4aaf1c50cb26f911d86e179f27af177a4e1d2ac","tid":1984133,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"妍雨不在了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341151ec0fedf0fef86a43f23a2952145d5d14c3","tid":1984133,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"大紀元內容農場post拉"},{"pid":"377ec04424af7338c5e3656fdb4887c7110659de","tid":1984133,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"341151ec0fedf0fef86a43f23a2952145d5d14c3","tid":1984133,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"大紀元內容農場post拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"大紀元反習要支持"},{"pid":"90f23bf997e4c003b9e471216ef65797a7723be2","tid":1984133,"uid":81725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"377ec04424af7338c5e3656fdb4887c7110659de","tid":1984133,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"341151ec0fedf0fef86a43f23a2952145d5d14c3","tid":1984133,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"大紀元內容農場post拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"大紀元反習要支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"你智商同大紀元D報導一樣低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b856462a559394200702468c92c209e903dee6","tid":1984133,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4aaf1c50cb26f911d86e179f27af177a4e1d2ac","tid":1984133,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"妍雨不在了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2